---
---

<section class="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-shell how-inner">
    <div class="how-header reveal">
      <p class="section-kicker">How it works</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Zero setup. Pure flow.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">
        No accounts, no new editors to learn. Just start a session and share the link.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step reveal r-d1">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Start in your surface</h3>
        <p>Run `shadow start .` from the CLI or launch a session directly from the VS Code sidebar.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal r-d2">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Shadow copies the key</h3>
        <p>The join command includes the E2E key, making it long by design. Shadow automatically handles the copy step.</p>
        <div class="code-block">
          <code>shadow join 'https://...#e2e-key'</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step reveal r-d3">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3>Both sides edit live</h3>
        <p>Not a screen share. Not editor lock-in. It's the same project updating in real time for everyone.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    margin-bottom: var(--gap);
  }

  .how-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .step p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .code-block {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--paper-strong);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .code-block code {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text);
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
